stall pm2-server-monit\n\n## Update to latest version\n\n    \n    \n    pm2 module:update pm2-server-monit\n\n## About\n\nMonitor server CPU / Memory / Process / Zombie Process / Disk size / Security\nPackages / Network Input / Network Output\n\nkeymetrics.io/\n\n### Topics\n\nalert cpu monitor module memory pm2 stats monit pm2-server-monit keymetrics\n\n### Resources\n\nReadme\n\n### License\n\nMIT license\n\nActivity\n\nCustom properties\n\n### Stars\n\n257 stars\n\n### Watchers\n\n13 watching\n\n### Forks\n\n37 forks\n\nReport repository\n\n## Releases 1\n\nv2.0 Latest\n\nJul 22, 2016\n\n## Packages 0\n\nNo packages published\n\n## Contributors 10\n\n## Languages\n\n  * JavaScript 98.0%\n  * Jsonnet 2.0%\n\n## Footer\n\n\u00a9 2024 GitHub, Inc.\n\nYou can\u2019t perform that action at this time.\n\n", "frontpage": false}
